Follow the best practices for Next.js
Use TailwindCSS for styling
styling should be responsive
custom css should be in the /styles folder
class or interface should be in the /types folder
follow DRY principle

Do not change unrelated code 
Do not remove commented code


before creating a new file, check if it already exists in the project
before creating a new component, check if it already exists in the project
before creating a new page, check if it already exists in the project
before creating a new route, check if it already exists in the project
before creating a new function, check if it already exists in the project

follow the folder structure
